OL,3,CTen babies die in fire at Indian
OL,4,Chospital
OL,6,FAn investigation is underway at a
OL,7,Fhospital in India following a fire
OL,8,Fwhich killed ten babies, as ITV News'
OL,9,FEllie Pitt reports
OL,11,FTen newborn babies have been killed by
OL,12,Fa fire which tore through a neonatal
OL,13,Fintensive care unit at a hospital in
OL,14,FIndia, authorities said.
OL,16,FThe fire occurred at a hospital in
OL,17,FJhansi city in northern India on
OL,18,FFriday night, with the blaze spreading
OL,19,Fquickly through the ward where 55
OL,20,Finfants were being treated.
