OL,4,Chospital
OL,6,F45 babies were rescued, with 16 of
OL,7,Fthose critically injured, but ten were
OL,8,Fkilled, said Bimal Kumar Dubey, a
OL,9,Flocal official.
OL,11,FAn initial investigation pointed to
OL,12,Flapses in safety protocols, including
OL,13,Fexpired fire extinguishers and non-
OL,14,Ffunctional fire alarms, which
OL,15,Fofficials say delayed rescue efforts.
